# Real .env files (git-ignored by this project's root .gitignore) hold
# secrets and per-environment values — never commit a real one.
#
# Its OWN dedicated schema — this mini-project adds/drops a real generated
# column and a real GIN index via raw SQL, so it needs full, isolated
# ownership of its schema, same reasoning as every other real-DDL mini-
# project in this codebase. See build-conventions.md.
DATABASE_URL="postgres://user:password@host:5432/postgres?schema=node_express_learning_indexing_search"
